On February 6, 2023, the 7.8 magnitude earthquake that struck Syria and TÃ¼rkiye took the world by surprise. 

This week, ANN features a deeper look into the impacts of this natural disaster and what ADRA International is doing to provide emergency assistance in the region. 

Watch as ANN highlights this story and reports on other news from around the world.
